This is only for the colibri VF50 Machine[It is work for Console-trdx-image]
- Removing all Graphics related support
- meta-colibri layer is working for both BSP as well as High level Application
- no need to add meta-fsl-arm or meta-fsl-arm-extra or meta-toradex layer in your bblayers.conf,just only meta-colibri layer is enough
- Added support of new latest linux-kernel-4.4,If you want to use it then set the version for the virtual/kernel and preferred provider,
    Ex. set in your local.conf
        PREFERRED_PROVIDER_virtual/kernel ?= "linux-toradex"
        PREFERRED_VERSION_linux-toradex ?= "4.4%"

